# Files the running app writes at runtime that must NOT trigger a `tauri dev`
# restart. `tauri dev` watches the whole src-tauri/ directory, and the dev binary's
# working directory IS src-tauri/ — so saving a document or exporting a mesh into
# the default (relative) path lands here. Without these ignores, that write makes
# the dev watcher kill + relaunch the app mid-session, closing the window and
# wiping the in-memory document (looks like a "crash on save", loses unsaved work).
*.sindri
*.stl
*.step
*.stp
*.3mf
*.obj
*.brep
